short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search and select from your open tabs by searching with command+p

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have too many tabs open and can't find the one you're looking for? 

Just search for it. 

This extension runs a fuzzy search across all your open tabs and returns a list of results. Click the tab you want in your results list and Chrome will jump to that tab. You can make it handier by binding a keystroke to the extension in your extension settings pane.

Please help improve it! https://github.com/conorsg/tab_p
